data.description: Stop the car!! This is the home that you have been dreaming of, located in a quant community on a small beautiful lake. This 3 bedroom, 3 bathroom home is just right for your family. When you walk through the front door, you are greeted with a tall foyer. Then there is a bedroom downstairs, that can be an in-law suite, bedroom, or office. Walk to the main living area and get blown away by the view of Lake Confusion right at your backyard. The kitchen, nook, living room combo is perfect for keeping the family connected. The screened in lanai is perfect for coffee, tea and a book. At the top of the stairs you will find a loft, again perfect for a second family-tv area. The owner's bedroom has wonderful views of the lake again, and then a huge walk-in closet past the bathroom. The second bedroom shares a bathroom with the loft. The laundry room is conveniently located upstairs - so no carrying loads up the flight of stairs. The home is just over a year old, so you get the benefits of a new home without the build time. If you are looking for the perfect home, this is it. Call your agent today to set up a viewing, and call this home yours!
